    &gt;Maven依赖版本查看&lt;/a&gt;|&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://maven.apache.org/download.cgi&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;
    &gt;Maven – Download&lt;/a&gt;|&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://archive.apache.org/dist/maven/maven-3/&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;
